===Etymology===
A late borrowing from the {{der|mul|grc|-}} letter {{m|grc|Œ•||ypsilon}}, first used to write Greek loanwords in Latin, derived from the {{der|mul|phn|-}} letter {{m|phn|ê§Ö||waw}}, from the {{der|mul|egy|-}} hieroglyph {{m|egy|ìè≤}}.
